title: Ricky Velez
itunes:title: Ricky Velez
description:
Comedian Ricky Velez (MASTER OF NONE, THE KING OF STATEN ISLAND) and Whitney ambush Machine Gun Kelly and Logan Paul with FaceTimes and talk about everything from Scientology to the NELK boys to 50 Cent gossip. Ricky's comedy special HERE'S EVERYTHING is streaming now on HBO.
